data.text: El ser @samuel_garcias simplemente es una copia vil y sin escrúpulos de Zapp Brannigan de Futurama ... un imbécil con poder y alguien que le hace todo.

entity.name: Futurama
entity.description: Accidentally frozen, pizza-deliverer Fry wakes up 1,000 years in the future. He is taken in by his sole descendant, an elderly and addled scientist who owns a small cargo delivery service. Among the other crew members are Capt. Leela, accountant Hermes, intern Amy, obnoxious robot Bender and lobsterlike moocher "Dr." Zoidberg.
